{"lemma": "ظَرِيفٌ", "slug": "ظَرِيفٌ", "root": "ظ.ر.ف", "root_slug": "ظ-ر-ف", "root_link": "/words/roots/ظ-ر-ف", "pos": "N", "pos_camel": "noun", "paradigm": [], "frequency_in_corpus": 0, "cross_references": {"qac": {"found": false}, "wiktextract": {"found": true, "entry_count": 1, "pos_tags": ["adj"], "has_etymology": true, "sense_count": 1}, "lanes": {"found": true, "entry_ids": ["n27545"], "search_url": "https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B8%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%81%D9%8C"}}, "translations": {"en": "charming, elegant", "fa": "ظریف، خوش‌ساخت", "ur": "ظریف، خوبصورت", "tr": "zarif, şık", "id": "menarik, elegan", "bn": "চালাক, সুন্দর", "es": "gracioso, elegante", "fr": "charmant, élégant", "de": "witzig, elegant", "ru": "остроумный, изящный", "zh": "风趣，优雅"}, "definition": {"source": "wiktextract", "senses": [{"pos": "adj", "gloss": "charming, elegant"}]}, "etymology": {"source": "wiktextract", "text": "فَعِيل (faʕīl)-type stative-verb derived from the active participle from the verb ظَرُفَ (ẓarufa)."}, "ipa": ["/ðˤa.riːf/"], "lanes_definition": {"source": "lanes", "entries": [{"entry_id": "n27545", "headword_ar": "ظَرِيفٌ", "root": "Zrf", "body": [{"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Possessing the quality,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "qualities, termed"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Zarof", "text_ar": "ظَرْف"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (T, S, M, O, Msb, K;) as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ZuraAfN", "text_ar": "ظُرَافٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (Lh, M, O, K,) the two being like"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "TawiylN", "text_ar": "طَوِيلٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "TuwaAlN", "text_ar": "طُوَالٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (O,) [or the latter has an intensive signification, (see"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "TuwaAlN", "text_ar": "طُوَالٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and see also the “ Durrat el-Ghowwás, ” in De Sacy's Anthol. Gramm. Arabe, p. 48 of the Ar. text,)] and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Zur~aAfN", "text_ar": "ظُرَّافٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (M, K,) or this last, which is like"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Tuw~aAlN", "text_ar": "طُوَّالٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", denotes more than"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ZuraAfN", "text_ar": "ظُرَافٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "without teshdeed: (O:) accord. to Mbr, it is derived from"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Zarof", "text_ar": "ظَرْف"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifying “ a receptacle, ” as though meaning a receptacle for excellence, or elegance, in mind, manners, or address or speech: (TA:) [it may be rendered, agreeably with explanations of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ZarofN", "text_ar": "ظَرْفٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "excellent,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "elegant, in mind, manners,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "address"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "speech;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in person, countenance"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "garb, guise,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "external appearance:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "clever, ingenious, intelligent,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "acute in intellect; well-mannered, well-bred, accomplished,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "polite; beautiful in person"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "countenance; elegant,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "graceful;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.:] and is expl. as meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "eloquent;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "thus by As and IAar: and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "possessing knowledge and courage:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "goodly,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "beautiful, in clothing,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in outer apparel:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA:) and is used by the people of El-Yemen as meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "skilful:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(O:) and, as Ks says, it is applied as an epithet to a tongue, and to a face: (TA:) the pl. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ZariyfN", "text_ar": "ظَرِيفٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ZiraAfN", "text_ar": "ظِرَافٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, M, O, Msb, K) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ZurafaA='u", "text_ar": "ظُرَفَا=ءُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(T, S, O, Msb, K) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Zariyfuwna", "text_ar": "ظَرِيفُونَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(O, K) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ZurufN", "text_ar": "ظُرُفٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, M, IB, K,) a form sometimes used, (IB, TA,) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ZuruwfN", "text_ar": "ظُرُوفٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (T, S, M, O, K,) also a form sometimes used, (S, O,) approvable in poetry, (T,) as though formed from"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ZarofN", "text_ar": "ظَرْفٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", or [anomalous] like"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ma*aAkiyru", "text_ar": "مَذَاكِيرُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, O, K) accord. to Kh (S, O) and Sb: (TA:) the pl. of ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ZuraAfN", "text_ar": "ظُرَافٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ZurafaA='u", "text_ar": "ظُرَفَا=ءُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (Lh, M, K:) and the pl. of ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Zur~aAfN", "text_ar": "ظُرَّافٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Zur~aAfuwna", "text_ar": "ظُرَّافُونَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (M, K:) the fem. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ZariyfN", "text_ar": "ظَرِيفٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ZariyfapN", "text_ar": "ظَرِيفَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; and the pl. of this is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ZiraAfN", "text_ar": "ظِرَافٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (Sb, T, M, Msb, TA,) like a pl. of the masc., (Sb, M, TA,) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ZaraAy^ifu", "text_ar": "ظَرَايِفُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (T, M, TA.) It is said in a trad. of 'Omar, mentioned by IAar, (Mgh, O, TA,) and by As, (TA,)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_i*aA kaAna All~iS~u ZariyfFA laA yuqoTaEu", "text_ar": "اـِذَا كَانَ اللِّصُّ ظَرِيفًا لَا يُقْطَعُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (Mgh,) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "lamo yuqoTaEo", "text_ar": "لَمْ يُقْطَعْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (O, TA,) meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "When the thief is eloquent"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Mgh, O, TA)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "and intelligent,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Mgh,) he averts from himself the prescribed punishment by his pleading [so that"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he will not be,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "is not, mutilated"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "by amputation of the hand]. (Mgh, O, TA.)"}], "source_refs": ["Lh", "M", "O", "K", "TA", "S", "Msb", "T", "IB", "Sb", "Mgh"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}